reviews.review_text:
Another matrix that works This show that has aud and sbd and has been in ciruclation for years. So I am not reviewing the actual show, just this release.  

This is a matrix that does not suffer from flanging effects. Some matrix sound terrible. This one is win.

I have one complaint. The songs are mislabeled (off by one) starting with track 2. This show ends with ujb.
